                     <interp inst="t17830115-18-punish123" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="newgate"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-18-defend230 t17830115-18-punish123"></join>
               imprisoned in Newgate six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
